{"tid":2511988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國多間球會和體育組織停用社交網絡　　指要阻止網上仇恨言論與歧視","createTime":"2021-05-01T10:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T10:33:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61c1ced219676e13d3a68eb77f0a8f91807056ef","tid":2511988,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/stop-online-hate.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2Fstop-online-hate.jpg&h=6be0ae12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n數小時前，大家都突然開始看到多個英超球會包括利物浦、阿仙奴、曼聯、車路士等，以及甚至乎英國電視台如Sky Sports等都突然出現#stoponlinehate的hashtag，又或類似的宣傳，指要阻止網上仇恨言論與歧視。這其實是英國多間體育相關的組織的最新抗議行動，指社交網絡管控言論不足，故此停用社交網絡4天，希望停止網上暴力，以更強硬手段阻止網上針對運動員的種族歧視和涉及性言論的暴力。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2021/05/stop-online-hate-campaign/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2021%2F05%2Fstop-online-hate-campaign%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRFLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=87a0608d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2021/05/stop-online-hate-campaign/</a>"}]}